window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Blake Turner had it all - until a demon decided to take residence in his soul. Plagued with constant black outs and a trail of dead bodies in his wake, Blake thinks vampire Elise is his best chance at ending the nightmare. It's just too bad he's fallen in love with the gorgeous vamp right before he has to die…. Featuring characters from <i>New York Times</i> best-selling author Jeaniene Frost's Night Huntress world. (Originally appeared in <i>Four Dukes and a Devil</i> anthology.)</p>"; 
